{"tid":514946,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"英超新兵盧卡古「對辦」梅開二度　曼聯開咧戰贏4球升榜首","createTime":"2017-12-31T04:14:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-01T07:51:13.000Z","uid":478,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0c1e062e843c67afb8ac81b10c7183214c102405","tid":514946,"uid":478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T04:14:36.000Z","msg":"有什麼好過入一球？就係入兩球！以天價加盟曼聯的中鋒盧卡古，在新一季英超開咧戰於主場梅開二度，加上馬迪爾及普巴分別建功，帶領「紅魔鬼」以4：0大破韋斯咸，更憑得失球差壓過哈特斯菲升上榜首。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">曼聯今屆多了中場尼曼查馬迪及前鋒盧卡古兩名新援後，連比賽風格也改變，一改去屆進攻緩慢的毛病，</span>甫開賽便推高比賽節奏，前場的桑馬達、米希達利恩、拉舒福特等不斷互相走位，拉開對手防線，盧卡古與普巴則以爆炸力衝擊對手，加上馬迪不時長傳分邊，讓兩翼兩閘皆有進攻機會，無疑紅魔鬼上半場的進攻表現非常「對辦」，雖然埋門只有6次，但控球率達67%，角球更是9：0之比，可謂佔盡優勢。<br />\n<br />\n身價高達7600萬鎊的盧卡古，雖然觸球機會不多，但18分鐘便有一次入球良機，可是他接應桑馬達左路傳中，但在兩名韋斯咸守將夾擊下，近門無法將皮球送入網窩。至33分鐘，馬迪中場截得皮球，拉舒福特策動反擊，直線妙傳與盧卡古勁射破網，打破缺口。易邊後僅7分鐘，盧卡古又有進帳，接應米希達利恩左路開出的罰球，近門輕鬆頂入成2：0。<br />\n馬迪爾後備入替一傳一射<br />\n<br />\n紅魔領先兩球後得勢不饒人，任左翼的拉舒福特表現尤為活躍，頻頻在邊線策動攻勢，盧卡古頂入的一球便是先由他博得犯規，之後他又兩度有入球機會，可是不是操之過急半單刀射斜，就是稍欠運氣勁射中柱。韋斯咸則只有零星攻勢，其中新加盟的阿拿奧杜域力壓戴利白蘭特一頂，但又頂中楣頂。<br />\n<br />\n另一年輕球員安東尼馬迪爾卻更有入球運，在80分鐘後備入替後，只用了7分鐘便把握單刀機會射成3：0；他3分鐘後又助攻普巴建功，助曼聯取得4：0大捷，更升上英超榜首。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"630fa1cee3cb4f0066ecf979e8f92289f3802fd7","tid":514946,"uid":13718,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T04:21:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e52ed4c331b9b1719aaa7d86db14ef3f8185c87","tid":514946,"uid":29820,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T05:05:04.000Z","msg":"好大陣精味<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75d1d6ec0d2a106e57cbcb8344641ee537a7e490","tid":514946,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T05:10:55.000Z","msg":"勁撚到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n尋晚肯定狂轟10球升埋上榜首啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f89473bb63f48c081dc9d9df2a445e1dfac96af6","tid":514946,"uid":31,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T05:46:38.000Z","msg":"有咩好過助攻一次 就係助攻兩次<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea3141b87d562f854e1553577bfc5ca2cf1a1c21","tid":514946,"uid":478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T06:21:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a5da4df41fc2e54b331c78d60b546208a9f3488","tid":514946,"uid":478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T05:51:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09a20c06031512e01ae5900b05f4817b3ad9c6e3","tid":514946,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T06:39:57.000Z","msg":"樓主衰咩坐左半年<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"063f75e5497a1400e57756856bc42acc38990ef3","tid":514946,"uid":19093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T07:17:44.000Z","msg":"樓主個名配合post 主題<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aac5cacc603b3fa0dbb022220ed2fa0c82ce600","tid":514946,"uid":478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T07:51:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/fa